OL,3,CWomen should be offered talking
OL,4,Ctherapy on NHS to ease menopause
OL,5,Csymptoms, Nice suggests
OL,7,FThe NHS should offer women talking
OL,8,Ftherapy to ease menopause symptoms,
OL,9,Faccording to new guidance.
OL,11,FEvidence from the National Institute
OL,12,Ffor Health and Care Excellence (Nice)
OL,13,Fshows that cognitive behavioural
OL,14,Ftherapy (CBT), which typically
OL,15,Finvolves talking through mental and
OL,16,Femotional issues, could help women to
OL,17,Fcombat symptoms such as hot flushes,
OL,18,Fnight sweats and disrupted sleep.
